author: penwhale/ソフ
text:
Japanese have different phrases for "over X"  and "X and above" [as well as "below X" vs "X and below"].
The phrase in question - 以下 - is the phrase for "X and below" - which for position purposes becomes "Xth place and below".
The title being 9位以下 - 9th place and below - therefore includes 9th place (meaning the stream ends if she gets 9th).





... The fact that she got 10th place made it moot anyway
